text.tspan: welcome to the new way of doing SCRUM on-line...
these features and more are just a few clicks away...

flowRoot.flowPara: As soon as you become a member of this open beta, you can start enjoying the experience.
Agilar Dev Team uses the taskboard daily and is spread across continents. Distributed enough for you? ;)
Working with SCRUM implies using prioritized backlogs. The Agilar Taskboard has its own built-in Product Backlog manager. Learn More.
A team with multiple projects? A project management nightmare? Immerse yourself in the inter-project prioritization with the Team View. Learn More.
Do you run multiple projects in your organization? Want a single tool to keep track of them all? The Agilar Taskboard is prepared to handle multiple projects per organization. Learn More
Working for an organization with lots of teams? Want to assign teams to specific projects? The Agilar Taskboard can do that! Learn More.
Do you work with a Product Owner not in your organization? Working with consultants? Take a look at the brand new Guest Member feature. Learn More.
